nh ngha d liu:
Name Dn expression
Name: Tn bin
Dn : Ch dn nh ngha cc thnh phn d liu
DB : Byte
DW: 1 T 2 bytes
DD: T kp 4 bytes
DF: 6 bytes
DQ : 4 t . 8 bytes
DT : 10 bytes
Expression: biu thc, c th cha du ?
V d:
A DB ? ; bin A cha c khi
to gi tr u
B DB 10011100B ;
C DB 10, 20, 30, 40, 100 ; mng 5
phn t
D DB 10 DUP(?) ; 10 bytes cha khi
to E DW 5 DUP(0) ; 5 t (2 bytes); Gi tr
mi t = 0;
0F1H
Truy nhp vo mng
1.
Mov al,c; al=10
Mov al,c+1; al=20
Mov al,c+2; al=30
Mov al,c+3; al=40
Mov al,c+4; al=100
2.
Lea si,1
Mov al, c[si]
Mov si,3
Mov al, c[si]
V d : truy cp mng C 5 phn t
MOV SI, 0
MOV CX, 5
DOC_MANG:
MOV AL, C[SI]
INC SI
LOOP DOC_MANG
Bi thc hnh:
Cho mng A c n phn t kiu byte c khi

gi tr > s P cho trc ;
3. Chn 1 gi tr Q vo v tr k ca mng.
